title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ and RP on New Community Combat Series
content:
Step into a curated collection of player-created Jobs built around gunplay, chaos, and tactical brawls in the Community Combat Series and earn 2X GTA$ and RP through August 20.

This week’s new Job is a King of the Hill built around the Up-n-Atomizer — expect plenty of rag dolling as you ascend a construction site to grab a laptop and score points for your team. Check out [Yo] Atomizer KOTH by joining the Community Combat Series from your iFruit, or by heading over to Legion Square.
